William C. URBANSKI, Appellant
v.
Marion O'MALLEY, Appellee No. 21 MAP 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. Decided: April 26, 2019

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 26 th day of April, 2019, Appellee's Application for Leave to File a Sur-Reply Brief is GRANTED, and the order of the Court of Common Pleas of Susquehanna County is hereby AFFIRMED. Appellee's Application for Leave to Present Oral Argument is DENIED as moot.
